name: Icon Design System - Tabler Icons
description:
Tabler Icons

A set of over 1250 free MIT-licensed high-quality SVG icons for you to use in your web projects. Each icon is designed on a 24x24 grid and a 2px stroke.


Icons search: https://tabler-icons.io/


License

Tabler Icons is licensed under the MIT License.


------------------------------------------------


I'm not the official creation team of Tabler Icons, just a fan who really likes and wants to share this amazing iconset.

Please check and support the official creator of Tabler Icons.

Thank you.
